#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn56.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Samādhivagga "
msgstr "1. Immersion "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Paṭhamakulaputtasutta "
msgstr "3. A Gentleman (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn56.3:1.1"
msgid "“Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ kulaputtā sammā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajiṃsu, sabbe te catunnaṃ ariyasaccānaṃ yathābhūtaṃ abhisamayāya. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, whatever gentlemen—past, "

msgctxt "sn56.3:1.2"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ kulaputtā sammā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajissanti, sabbe te catunnaṃ ariyasaccānaṃ yathābhūtaṃ abhisamayāya. "
msgstr "future, "

msgctxt "sn56.3:1.3"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi kulaputtā sammā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, sabbe te catunnaṃ ariyasaccānaṃ yathābhūtaṃ abhisamayāya. "
msgstr "or present—rightly go forth from the lay life to homelessness, all of them do so in order to truly comprehend the four noble truths. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn56.3:2.1"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn56.3:2.2"
msgid "Dukkhassa ariyasaccassa dukkhasamudayassa ariyasaccassa dukkhanirodhassa ariyasaccassa dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya ariyasaccassa. "
msgstr "The noble truths of suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering. "

msgctxt "sn56.3:2.3"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ kulaputtā sammā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajiṃsu … pe … "
msgstr "Whatever gentlemen—past, "

msgctxt "sn56.3:2.4"
msgid "pabbajissanti … pe … "
msgstr "future, "

msgctxt "sn56.3:2.5"
msgid "pabbajanti, sabbe te imesaṃyeva catunnaṃ ariyasaccānaṃ yathābhūtaṃ abhisamayāya. "
msgstr "or present—rightly go forth from the lay life to homelessness, all of them do so in order to truly comprehend the four noble truths. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn56.3:3.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo, ‘ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ti yogo karaṇīyo, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ti yogo karaṇīyo, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation to understand: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering’.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.3:3.2"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

